<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Set as default</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon blue"><i class="material-toggle_on"></i></span> = When you open the menu <strong>Item » Item UI</strong>, the filter settings will already be selected and the search will automatically start with these settings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon "><i class="material-toggle_off"></i></span> = The filter settings will not already be selected.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Create filter for all users</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon blue"><i class="material-toggle_on"></i></span> = The filter preset will be visible for all user accounts.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon "><i class="material-toggle_off"></i></span> = The filter preset will only be visible for your own user account.</p>
</div></div></td>
