<div class="paragraph">
<p>When you click on <strong>Saved filters</strong> (<span class="icon "><i class="material-bookmarks"></i></span>), you’ll see post-processing options for the filter:</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon "><i class="material-drag_indicator"></i></span> = Use drag &amp; drop to arrange the filter presets in a specific order.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon "><i class="material-delete"></i></span> = Deletes the filter preset.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-star-o  "></i></span> = Sets the filter as default.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="400">2.2. Applying saved filters</h3>
<div class="olist arabic">
