<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-gear  "></i></span></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Which columns should be included in the overview?</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Configure columns</strong> (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-gear  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select all of the desired columns (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-check-square  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>CONFIRM</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><span class="icon "><i class="material-drag_indicator"></i></span></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div class="content"><div class="paragraph">
<p>Which order should the columns be displayed in?</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Configure columns</strong> (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-gear  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Move your mouse cursor over an entry with the symbol <span class="icon "><i class="material-drag_indicator"></i></span>.<br>
→ Your mouse cursor changes shape (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-arrows  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Drag the entry to the desired spot.</p>
</li>
