</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Items are left-aligned.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Variations are indented.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>The currently selected level is displayed in blue font.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
